{"tid":1501263,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[列陣+反間]原地踏步只會固步自封 ！ ！ ！","createTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:23:42.000Z","uid":107157,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d994d9443d44f39c0904af2f47bbcea79226035a","tid":1501263,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Don't take it for granted<br />\n每次出黎遊行既機會都係靠文宣組努力宣傳先有今日既成果！ <br />\n所以要珍惜每次出黎既機會。<br />\n就算失敗，返去都要吸取教訓。<br />\n每一個下次都唔容許再犯上一次既錯誤！ ！</span></span> <br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成個行動既成敗就係喺前線。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">無論後面有幾多億人，前面頂唔住，後面就會不攻而破 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以</span></span>，前線要係top of the top，要有齊最好既裝備同列陣戰略知識，做好反間行動同列陣就唔會輸。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">前線反間重點:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1。 盡量以小隊形式進行</span></span><br />\n盡量搵相熟朋友組隊，最好雙數人數，可以互相幫助同監督。若果一次行動入面發現係鬼，立即記低資料同割席。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">2。 2隊小隊要有一個common groupmate</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">3。 禁止一個人私底下用通訊工具，要有人監督下先可以使用</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">列陣:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1。當與防線對恃狀態: <br />\n回字形陣式</span><br />\n<br />\n分<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span><span style=\"color: green;\">綠</span>2隊，<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>戰術要求比較高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>4人一組<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色</span>2人一組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aBdOtrm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaBdOtrm.jpg&h=9d403fe2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>小隊構造:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j0ExU8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj0ExU8o.jpg&h=2313e2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Commander: </span><br />\n唯一一個有視野既人。<br />\n捉實Blind Pusher。<br />\n提供視野資訊比其餘3人。<br />\n根據情況落order push/擋/走。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">Blind Pusher: </span><br />\n唯一一個可以推鐵馬既人。<br />\n冇視野。<br />\n聽Commander落order去推。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">Protector:</span><br />\n唯二有遮既人。<br />\n一手渣遮，一手捉實Blind pusher。<br />\n聽order用遮擋/拎開遮睇視野。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2。速龍小隊出動時:<br />\n 凹字型陣式</span><br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span>小隊即刻退後<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aRNrZE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaRNrZE4.jpg&h=6912da2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.速龍入黎既話，前方既<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色</span>小隊左右包抄<br />\n3.後方<span style=\"color: green;\">綠色</span>小隊上前補位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LHHGOyv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLHHGOyv.jpg&h=49eeec14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後面既支援小隊(滅煙，救援，物資等等)要隨時stand by</span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家有咩建議一齊討論！ ！ ！"},{"pid":"77feee00745f6af5557c1e9b623ef127ad4e00d5","tid":1501263,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">柯屎要紙巾 ！<br />\n遊行要列陣 ！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ac1c3ddd001be35f08925c02ab4bd8eb8a4e2f97","tid":1501263,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/